data.description: MLS# 272081 If you ever dreamed of owning a home, now's the time!!! Newly added solar panels will makes this home one of the most affordable on the Market!!! $21 a month Average for your power bills! Outdoor living with the covered front porch and a pergola in the back yard. This one level home in South Kennewick features an open concept with oak hardwood floors.  Three bedrooms, 2 baths, formal dining area (or another flex space) A den off the living room offers extra space for your home office, playroom, or even an exercise room. Fully fenced with a 2 car garage and security system.
